[NATSU] That's enough!

332
00:13:26,958 --> 00:13:28,625
It's time to
switch partners.

333
00:13:28,708 --> 00:13:30,000
My, what an enchanting

334
00:13:30,083 --> 00:13:31,291
gentleman you are.

335
00:13:31,375 --> 00:13:32,625
It's actually kind
of funny you would

336
00:13:32,708 --> 00:13:36,583
put it that way, cause this
is a magic user's ball.

337
00:13:36,666 --> 00:13:38,541
So what kind of
magic do you use?

338
00:13:38,625 --> 00:13:40,000
That is a rather
personal question

339
