don't you think?

340
00:13:41,500 --> 00:13:43,875
A true gentleman would
reveal his type of magic first

341
00:13:43,958 --> 00:13:45,250
before asking a lady.

342
00:13:45,333 --> 00:13:47,625
Ha, I guess the whole
'being a gentleman' thing

343
00:13:47,708 --> 00:13:49,541
ain't really my strong suit.

344
00:13:49,625 --> 00:13:51,333
I see, well I suppose
I'll play along

345
00:13:51,416 --> 00:13:53,083
and show you mine first.

346
00:13:53,166 --> 00:13:54,541
Maker magic.

347
00:13:54,625 --> 00:13:56,291
Ice Make Swan!

348
00:13:57,250 --> 00:14:00,666
So you just happen to
use the same kinda magic I do?

349
00:14:00,750 --> 00:14:02,333
Now, Ice Make

350
00:14:02,416 --> 00:14:03,916
Kite!

351
