Very impressive,
but not my style.

352
00:14:14,083 --> 00:14:15,708
Ice Make Polar bear!

353
00:14:18,416 --> 00:14:20,583
Ice Make Prison Cell!

354
00:14:22,625 --> 00:14:23,708
You really know how to show

355
00:14:23,791 --> 00:14:25,250
a lady a good time.

356
00:14:25,333 --> 00:14:27,208
Ice Make Bazooka!

357
00:14:27,291 --> 00:14:29,416
If you think
that's fun, try this.

358
00:14:29,500 --> 00:14:31,000
Ice Make Cannon!

359
