completely off the rails.

365
00:14:44,875 --> 00:14:47,625
Look, Miss Aceto's
up on the balcony.

366
00:15:14,041 --> 00:15:16,416
It would appear that all
the men here are intimidated

367
00:15:16,500 --> 00:15:18,375
by my daughter's beauty.

368
00:15:18,458 --> 00:15:21,291
The way you sparkle
is so manly!

369
00:15:21,375 --> 00:15:23,458
I am a girl,
you know.

370
00:15:23,541 --> 00:15:24,791
Now then.

371
00:15:24,875 --> 00:15:26,958
Would you grant me the
honor of the first dance?

372
00:15:27,041 --> 00:15:28,291
Of course.

373
00:15:32,166 --> 00:15:33,583
Why in the heck is
the Count's daughter

374
00:15:33,666 --> 00:15:35,541
dancing with Erza?

375
00:15:35,625 --> 00:15:37,333
I don't know!

376
00:15:37,416 --> 00:15:38,666
[YOUNG MALE GUEST]
Excuse me, Miss.

377
00:15:38,750 --> 00:15:40,625
May I have this dance?

378
