00:15:55,041 --> 00:16:00,708
[clock chimes]

385
00:16:00,791 --> 00:16:02,166
Now what's
goin' on?

386
00:16:02,250 --> 00:16:04,375
The fateful
hour is upon us.

387
00:16:04,458 --> 00:16:07,000
[ERZA] And what
happens at midnight?

388
00:16:07,083 --> 00:16:08,458
The ring is presented.

389
00:16:08,541 --> 00:16:09,833
The bells within that giant,

390
00:16:09,916 --> 00:16:13,291
old clock only toll on one
night every seven years.

391
00:16:13,375 --> 00:16:16,208
When the doors open,
out comes the ring.

392
00:16:16,291 --> 00:16:18,333
[BALSAMICO] Whoever takes
