family tradition!

395
00:16:24,583 --> 00:16:26,625
Anybody that takes
the ring can propose?

396
00:16:26,708 --> 00:16:29,291
[alarm rings]

397
00:16:31,958 --> 00:16:33,125
Do you boys
see that?

398
00:16:33,208 --> 00:16:34,791
I'll go check it out!

399
00:16:34,875 --> 00:16:36,250
I'm coming with you!

400
00:16:37,291 --> 00:16:38,583
