403
00:16:44,041 --> 00:16:46,041
[ELFMAN] I bet she won't
say no to a real man!

404
00:16:46,125 --> 00:16:47,833
Did you forget that
we're not here to hook up

405
00:16:47,916 --> 00:16:49,375
with the client's daughter?

406
00:16:54,000 --> 00:16:55,791
