00:17:18,375 --> 00:17:21,458
[VELVENO] Sky Dragon, Roar!

417
00:17:27,041 --> 00:17:28,500
[VELVENO] And now the
Balsamico family's

418
00:17:28,583 --> 00:17:31,916
