of the one and only Velveno!

419
00:17:32,000 --> 00:17:33,083
He did it.

420
00:17:33,166 --> 00:17:34,208
Why you
rotten thief!

421
00:17:34,291 --> 00:17:35,708
Give it back
this instant!

422
00:17:35,791 --> 00:17:36,750
[NATSU] Alright!

423
00:17:36,833 --> 00:17:37,958
This party's finally
gettin' started!

424
00:17:38,041 --> 00:17:39,791
