425
00:17:39,875 --> 00:17:42,041
Fire Dragon Iron Fist!

426
00:17:43,291 --> 00:17:44,958
Fire Dragon Iron Fist!

427
00:17:45,041 --> 00:17:46,166
What?

428
00:17:49,208 --> 00:17:50,791
[NATSU] Fire Dragon Roar!

429
00:17:50,875 --> 00:17:53,458
[VELVENO] Fire Dragon Roar!

430
00:17:58,250 --> 00:17:59,166
Ha!

431
00:17:59,250 --> 00:18:00,625
