437
00:18:10,000 --> 00:18:11,791
We're men!

438
00:18:11,875 --> 00:18:13,291
Requip!

439
00:18:14,166 --> 00:18:15,625
Purgatory Armor!

440
00:18:15,708 --> 00:18:16,625
Requip.

441
00:18:16,708 --> 00:18:18,000
Purgatory Armor!

442
00:18:22,416 --> 00:18:24,125
It's pointless!

443
00:18:24,208 --> 00:18:27,000
