butt the old fashioned way.

447
00:18:35,291 --> 00:18:37,166
And we're pretty
good at it, ya know!

448
00:18:38,166 --> 00:18:39,416
Aw, knock it off!

449
00:18:39,500 --> 00:18:41,250
