tonight is get in a brawl

450
00:18:41,333 --> 00:18:42,500
with you and your buddies.

451
00:18:42,583 --> 00:18:43,583
[NATSU] Say what?

452
00:18:43,666 --> 00:18:45,750
I'm here 'cause
I screwed up last time.

453
00:18:45,833 --> 00:18:48,541
I've waited seven long
years to try it out again.

454
00:18:50,625 --> 00:18:51,708
Aceto.

455
00:18:51,791 --> 00:18:54,250
I've got something
big to ask you.

456
00:18:57,250 --> 00:18:58,916
No way!

457
00:18:59,000 --> 00:19:00,791
We've known each other
ever since we were both

458
00:19:00,875 --> 00:19:02,500
just little kids.

459
00:19:02,583 --> 00:19:06,791
And this entire time, I've
been crazy in love with you.

460
00:19:06,875 --> 00:19:08,541
You were the low-born
child of one of my

461
