he tried to visit.

470
00:19:26,375 --> 00:19:29,083
And you don't need to hear
about any of this now!

471
00:19:29,166 --> 00:19:30,875
The sad thing is,
I started to believe him

472
00:19:30,958 --> 00:19:34,041
and decided I was finally
gonna give up on you, Aceto.

473
00:19:34,125 --> 00:19:36,791
I kinda gave up on
myself too, I drifted around

474
00:19:36,875 --> 00:19:39,833
for a while, and eventually
turned to a life o' crime.

475
00:19:39,916 --> 00:19:41,250
I got arrested.

476
00:19:41,333 --> 00:19:43,250
Ended up in jail.

477
00:19:43,333 --> 00:19:45,375
I'm not buyin' any
of this guy's crap.

478
00:19:45,458 --> 00:19:46,958
Wait.

479
00:19:47,041 --> 00:19:48,708
And while I was locked up.

480
00:19:48,791 --> 00:19:50,625
