pay for your crimes.

503
00:20:51,333 --> 00:20:52,708
You're right.

504
00:21:02,000 --> 00:21:03,625
Isn't it wonderful?

505
00:21:04,458 --> 00:21:05,625
That was so
beautiful!

506
00:21:05,708 --> 00:21:07,250
He's the
sweetest guy ever.

507
00:21:07,333 --> 00:21:08,625
Incredible.

508
00:21:08,708 --> 00:21:09,458
Yeah.

509
00:21:09,541 --> 00:21:11,000
That was so freakin' manly!

510
00:21:11,083 --> 00:21:13,416
I don't know
about all this.

511
00:21:13,500 --> 00:21:15,541
A round of applause
for the couple.

512
00:21:26,583 --> 00:21:28,291
Well, they're
haulin' me off.

513
00:21:28,375 --> 00:21:29,458
