531
00:22:23,125 --> 00:22:23,666
Oh.

532
00:22:23,750 --> 00:22:24,875
That's really great.

533
00:22:25,833 --> 00:22:27,083
It's so nice here.

534
00:22:27,166 --> 00:22:29,458
